description: Located on the prestigious East Side, just steps from the beach, this meticulously maintained 2-bed, 2-bath home offers soaring ceilings & an open-concept layout filled with natural light. The gourmet kitchen, with stainless steel appliances & a gas stove, seamlessly flowing into the living area with a gas fireplace and ample space for a large sectional sofa. The main suite with bay windows invite the morning sun, complemented by a built-in closet & an en-suite bathroom marble finishes & a rain shower. The second bedroom features a built-in closet & comfortably fits a queen-size bed; currently utilized as a home office. Step outside to your private deck, spacious enough for a dining table, grill, & lounge chair. Enhancing the home’s appeal is a private downstairs area, presently configured as a home gym equipped with a Peloton, elliptical, bench, & additional storage, yet easily adaptable as an office. Additional features include central AC, in-unit laundry & hardwood floors throughout
